stock.controller

Class StockController

  • java.lang.Object
    • stock.controller.StockController
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IStockController

    public class StockController
extends java.lang.Object
implements IStockController
    This class implements the controller interface IStockController. It implements method to control the full working of the program. It parses commands and delegates the processing to their respective command classes. Entering 'q' or 'quit' terminates the program. Asks to re-enter a command if syntax is incorrect.
